\v 1 Siye ngaphi isithandwa sakho, wena omuhle phakathi kwabesifazana? Siphendukele ngaphi isithandwa sakho, ukuze sisidinge kanye lawe\x + 1.8.\x*?
\v 2 Isithandwa sami sehlele esivandeni saso\x + 4.16. 5.1.\x*, emibhedeni yamakha\x + 5.13.\x*, ukudla ezivandeni, lokukha imiduze\x + 2.1.\x*.
\v 3 Ngingowesithandwa sami, lesithandwa sami singesami\x + 2.16.\x*, esidla phakathi kwemiduze\x + 2.1.\x*.
