\v 4 Umuhle, mthandwa wami\x + 1.15.\x*, njengeTiriza\x + Josh. 12.24. 1 Kho. 14.17.\x*, uyabukeka njengeJerusalema\x + 1.5.\x*, uyesabeka njenge\add butho\x + 6.10. Hab. 1.7.\x*\add* eliphethe iziboniso\x + 5.10.\x*.
\v 5 Susa amehlo akho kimi ngoba ayanginqoba. Inwele zakho zinjengomhlambi wembuzi zisehla eGileyadi\x + 4.1.\x*.
\v 6 Amazinyo akho anjengomhlambi wezimvukazi ezikhuphuka ekugezisweni, okuthi zonke zazo zizele amaphahla, njalo kungekho eyinyumba phakathi kwazo\x + 4.2.\x*.
\v 7 Inhlafuno zakho phakathi kweveyili lakho zinjengocezu \w lwepomegranati\w**\x + 4.3.\x*.
\v 8 Kukhona izindlovukazi ezingamatshumi ayisithupha, labafazi abancane abangamatshumi ayisificaminwembili\x + 3.7. 6.9.\x*, lezintombi ezingelanani\x + Hlab. 45.9,14.\x*.
\v 9 Linye ijuba lami\x + 2.14.\x*, opheleleyo wami\x + 5.2.\x*, nguye yedwa kunina, ongokhethiweyo wakhe\x + 6.10. 2 Joha. 1.\x* owamzalayo\x + Zaga 17.25.\x*. Amadodakazi ambona, ambusisa\x + Gen. 30.13.\x*, izindlovukazi labafazi abancinyane, bambabaza\x + 3.7. 6.9.\x*.
