\v 11 Ngehlela esivandeni senkelo ukubona okuhlumayo esigodini\x + Jobe 8.12. Dan. 4.12,14,21.\x*, ukubona ukuthi ivini liyahluma\x + 7.12.\x*, \w amapomegranati\w**\x + 4.3.\x*\x + 7.12.\x* ayakhahlela yini\x + Tshu. 12.5.\x*.
\v 12 Ngingakazi umphefumulo wami wangimisa \add e\add*zinqol\add eni\add* zobukhosi zabantu bakithi\f + \fl kumbe \fq Ami-Nadibi.\f*\x + 2 Kho. 2.12. 13.14.\x*.
