\v 13 Phenduka, phenduka, mShulami\x + 1 Kho. 1.3,2 Kho. 4.12.\x*, phenduka, phenduka, ukuze sikubuke. Limbukelani umShulami? Kunjengexuku lamabutho amabili\x + Jer. 31.4.\x*\f + \fk amabutho amabili, \fl kumbe \fq Mahanayimi.\f*.
